thread.title: Obama vetoes $612 billion defense bill in rebuke to GOP

title: Obama vetoes $612 billion defense bill in rebuke to GOP
text:
> Political Obama vetoes $612 billion defense bill in rebuke to GOP President Barack Obama vetoes the National Defense Authorization Act (NDAA), Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015, in the Oval Office of the White House in Washington. The president vetoed the sweeping $612 billion defense policy bill, citing objections over how the measure is funded. (AP Photo/Susan Walsh) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
